[thinking] 
[thinking] I'm pondering the native-image agent access filter and the order of rules. If I exclude all first, could that mean everything gets excluded? But what about the existing generated metadata? I think tests might need to run in the JVM first, then the agent. I'm also questioning if this filter is specifically for the "caller" filter. It feels tricky because if I exclude everything first, does that mean I can't include anything later?
